opam-version: "2.0"
synopsis: "Cohttp client using Curl & Async as the backend"
description: """
An HTTP client that relies on Curl + Async for the backend. Does not require
conduit for SSL."""
maintainer: ["Anil Madhavapeddy <anil@recoil.org>"]
